event: message_saved
data: {"messageId":"XXP1fiDmRORLxYmntZZbm","role":"user","content":"Perform a comprehensive database forensics audit. Execute ALL of these queries using MCP tools:\n\n1. POSTGRESQL FORENSICS:\n   - Use admin_system_postgres_list_tables to enumerate all tables\n   - Use admin_system_postgres_raw_query: SELECT tablename, pg_size_pretty(pg_total_relation_size(schemaname||'.'||tablename)) AS size, n_live_tup AS rows FROM pg_stat_user_tables ORDER BY pg_total_relation_size(schemaname||'.'||tablename) DESC LIMIT 20\n   - Use admin_system_postgres_raw_query: SELECT u.email, COUNT(cs.id) as session_count, MAX(cs.\"updatedAt\") as last_active FROM \"User\" u LEFT JOIN \"ChatSession\" cs ON u.id = cs.\"userId\" GROUP BY u.email ORDER BY session_count DESC LIMIT 10\n   - Use admin_system_postgres_raw_query: SELECT role, COUNT(*) as count, AVG(LENGTH(content)) as avg_length FROM \"ChatMessage\" GROUP BY role\n   - Use admin_system_postgres_raw_query: SELECT name, value FROM \"SystemConfiguration\" WHERE name LIKE '%slider%' OR name LIKE '%model%' OR name LIKE '%provider%' ORDER BY name\n\n2. REDIS FORENSICS:\n   - Use admin_system_redis_health_check\n   - Use admin_system_redis_list_keys_by_pattern with pattern 'session:*' to check active sessions\n   - Use admin_system_redis_list_keys_by_pattern with pattern 'rate:*' to check rate limiting keys\n   - Use admin_system_redis_list_keys_by_pattern with pattern 'cache:*' to check cached data\n\n3. MILVUS FORENSICS:\n   - Use admin_system_milvus_health_check\n   - Use admin_system_milvus_list_collections\n   - For each collection found, use admin_system_milvus_get_collection_info\n\n4. SYNTHESIS:\n   - Total data volume across all stores\n   - User activity patterns\n   - Data growth rate estimation\n   - Storage optimization recommendations\n   - Any data integrity concerns\n\nExecute EVERY query and present actual results, not summaries.","timestamp":"2026-02-20T22:05:33.101Z","source":"database","confirmed":true}

